Cerepyrun
---------

An easy way to run python scripts (like the ones in cerebrum/config) with the
Cerebrum environment, as set up in ~/.cerebrumrc.

Examples:

  cerepyrun ~/checkout/cerebrum/contrib/populate-automatic-groups.py --help
  CI=uia cerepyrun ~/checkout/cerebrum/contrib/notes_full.py --logger-name console --help
 

